  "text": "Thermoacoustic instabilities are a major challenge for the reliable operation of many technical combustion systems, as reviewed by [CITATION_1] and references therein. For most practical applications with low-Mach number combustion, thermoacoustic phenomena can be modelled by an inhomogeneous Helmholtz equation, which reads",
